comment1.text=\r\n\ Create\ a\ player\ with\ a\ name\ and\ a\ starting\ room.\r\n\ @param\ pName\ the\ player\ name\ (can\ be\ empty\ or\ null)\r\n\ @param\ pStartRoom\ the\ initial\ room\r\n
