comment3.text=\r\n\ Change\ the\ current\ room,\ saving\ the\ previous\ one.\r\n\ This\ is\ called\ by\ the\ GameEngine\ after\ it\ validates\ the\ direction.\r\n\ @param\ pNextRoom\ the\ room\ to\ move\ to\r\n
